video_title: When You Feel Lost, Watch This
transcript:
if a problem is fixable then there's no
need to worry if it's not fixable then
there's no help in worrying there is no
benefit in worrying whatsoever sometimes
things seem uncertain and you find
yourself anxiously worrying about the
future take a deep breath repeat to
yourself there is no obstacle thrown in
my way that I won't be able to handle
understand that you cannot be prepared
for everything and that things may not
always go as planned and that's okay
